.TH PKGINSTALL 1M "2026-07-03" "Heirloom Darwin port" "Package Administration"
.SH NAME
pkginstall \- internal install helper for pkgadd
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pkginstall
.I "internal-args"
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B pkginstall
is an internal helper program invoked by
.BR pkgadd (1M).
End users should not invoke
.B pkginstall
directly. Its command line, environment, and exit codes are
subject to change without notice.
.SH HEIRLOOM DARWIN PORT
Supports the shared modality flags. See
.BR heirloom-modality (7).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR pkgadd (1M),
.BR pkgchk (1M),
.BR pkginfo (1).
